{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984180/extras/barrita2.png?t=1738666753\" /><br><br><strong>NIPA</strong> is a <strong>DUNGEON CRAWLER</strong> puzzle game with an oriental setting in which <strong>YOU CAN'T SHOOT</strong>.<br><br>Move, run, dodge, slow down time or transform into a ghost.<strong>NIPA will test the reflexes of the most skilled players</strong>. The only way to beat each level is repetition and perfection. The White Tower is a place full of obstacles and dangers that will delight those looking for a challenge.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984180/extras/gif2.gif?t=1738666753\" /><br><br>With a<strong> aesthetic inspired by Hindu culture</strong> and a dynamic <strong>soundtrack</strong> in which each piece accompanies the level, NIPA will transcend players to another astral plane, one in which self-improvement plays a key role.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984180/extras/gif1.gif?t=1738666753\" /><br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong><br><br>\u25cf Explore the White Tower and use your skills to dodge <strong>hundreds of bullets and enemies</strong>.<br>\u25cf Prepare to <strong>reincarnate</strong> over and over again until you beat the level.<br>\u25cf Take on puzzles against the clock and<strong>challenge your reflexes</strong>.<br>\u25cf 7 unique levels inspired by <strong>the chakras of the body</strong>, symbolising physical, mental, emotional and spiritual aspects.<br>\u25cf A Hindu setting with <strong>a pacifist message</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984180/extras/barrita1.png?t=1738666753\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984180/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738666753","background_raw